      <title>加拿大麦吉尔大学关闭校园，结束长达数月的加沙抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/canada-s-mcgill-shuts-campus-to-end-monthslong-protest-over-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦吉尔大学暂时关闭了位于蒙特利尔的主校区，试图驱逐在那里露营两个多月的亲巴勒斯坦抗议者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/canada-s-mcgill-shuts-campus-to-end-monthslong-protest-over-gaza</guid>
